name: Europa
description: Think of Project Europa as a new planet. As with any new territory, you need a passport to enter--that's our NFTs. Once you're in, you can start investing in collectors that will slowly accumulate ORBIT for you. But our planet is special--the longer you're on the planet and the more you play on the planet, the more ORBIT your collectors accumulate! Passive income meets interactivity. That's what Project Europa is about.
